title: Stella McCartney 'rear-ends' taxi driver then drives off | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad Get back! Stella McCartney drives away from scene of accident without leaving her details after 'rear-ending' taxi driver The 45-year-old daughter of The Beatles star Paul McCartney hit Asrah Nabezadeh's vehicle with her Mini Cooper in Hammersmith, West London When the cabbie got out of his car and began to film the damage, she drove off He followed her and recorded argument where she refused to give her details She eventually took his number and details were exchanged over the phone
